text: Laisamis is a settlement in Kenya's Marsabit County. In Laisamis there is a Catholic church dedicated to St George. It is the 5th largest urban centre in Marsabit County with a population of 2,643. The Isiolo-Moyale Highway passes through Laisamis. == References == Category:Populated places in Marsabit County
title: Laisamis
